{"tid":1773124,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"128【曼市打吡】蘇B：曼聯依舊是曼徹斯特一哥","createTime":"2019-12-07T08:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T04:08:32.000Z","uid":37875,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c339ad5f9b0b69f6b1e91f4ce5db09600448bcb2","tid":1773124,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:29:09.000Z","msg":"英國BBC報道，周六上演的曼市打吡賽前，兩軍領隊就那一支球隊是曼徹斯特一哥各有意見，其中曼聯領隊蘇斯克查，被問及曼城已經準備好，連續七季英超成績比曼聯好，這是自1930年以來從未發生過，到底曼聯是否仍比對方強大時，蘇B仍然嘴硬稱「是的」，但蘇B再補充：「毫無疑問目前我們大落後，但我們可以怎麼樣？放棄？不去挑戰他們嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n當然若用獎盃計算的話，曼城仍需要花很長時間才能追上曼聯，曼城領隊哥迪奧拿則稱：「對於曼聯球迷來說，他們永遠覺得曼聯是最偉大球會，但對於曼城球迷來說，他們則認為曼城是最偉大球會，這不關乎過去有多成功，這是你自身的感覺。」<br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿續指：「我了解過曼城的球會歷史，在最差最差的時候，球迷的支持度甚至比現在高。如果你觀看獎盃數量，無疑曼聯是更好，數字就是數字。但一直長時間努力支持球會的曼城球迷來說，曼城永遠是較佳。」"},{"pid":"96d6d6c9f5184d5531772f54f46edd315f3c172f","tid":1773124,"uid":2612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4